ng use of two inputs from recent studies of scaled Brownian LPP; namely,\nBrownian regularity of profiles, and estimates on the rarity of pairs of\ndisjoint scaled maximizing paths that begin and end close to each other.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2019 00:40:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Apr 2019 22:50:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 28 May 2019 21:26:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-30"}
