 state-of-the-art methods by more than 20\\% in\nretrieval performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2019 12:33:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 02:31:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-21"}
