 prior work. Moreover, SANNS is the\nfirst work that scales to the database of 10 million entries, pushing the limit\nby more than two orders of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2019 14:38:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 08:53:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2019 15:41:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2019 08:15:50 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sun, 8 Mar 2020 23:59:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-10"}
