ur findings suggest that people may\nnot always be prepared to deal with the unexpected consequences of DTC genetic\ntesting. Moreover, it appears that the users in this subreddit might not\nsufficiently consider privacy when taking a test or seeking an interpretation\nfrom a third-party service provider.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Apr 2019 15:43:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-04"}
